   <title><![CDATA[Christian Combat w/Michael Thiessen [The Ezra Institute Podcast for Cultural Reformation]]]></title>
   <link>https://app.dropwave.io/episode/23fcfc6b-35b7-4b0d-a979-67916e7bf1c2/christian-combat-wmichael-thiessen.mp3</link>
